column5: Good Morning All  Well after years of hunting the same area we feel we have finally figured out the master key to the whole area and the payoff was good quality time spent with friends lots of laughs and a supply of meat for the winter....... Priceless. Partridge coyotes and rabbits on deck  Special thanks to LUC V  PS nice little buck for your daughter TJ  Cheers Peter  gene pool tweaking 1  gene pool tweaking 2 + 2 more pictures to follow
Decent young bucks you guys got, glad to see you filled your tags. I know around by where I hunt it was crazy with shots this year, but I still managed to fill my tag too Congrats
